Name: Bones
Title: The Bikini in the Soup
Desc: The team investigates liquefied remains of a wedding planner, found in a tanning bed.
LongDescription: When the liquefied remains of a wedding planner are found in a tanning bed on Valentine's Day, Cam pressures the team to work fast so she can spend the holiday with her boyfriend; Clark helps Hodgins realize the best gifts come from the heart.
